data.description: Classic bungalow style home with beautiful front porch.  Newly renovated kitchen with laundry directly off of the kitchen. Two bedrooms and one bathroom, with a large living room and large formal dining room, plus a mudroom off of the side entrance.  There is a large unfinished basement with sump pump.  This home sits on a large lot with a nice back deck to relax on after a long day.  There is a large 2 car garage with a recent addition, that could possibly fit up to 3 vehicles.  The garage is partially insulated and ready for your finishing touches.
